lead_paragraph: After winning an Olympic gold medal, scoring five goals in his first six Brazil appearances and signing for Manchester City, Gabriel Jesus is looking to cap an unforgettable year this weekend with a Brazilian league title.

headline.print_headline: Man City's New Brazilian Sensation Looking to Cap Dream Year
